RainbruRPG::Gui::ServerDesc

RainbruRPG::Gui::ServerDesc Class Reference

#include <serverdesc.h>

List of all members.

Detailed Description

The xident description server dialog.

It is used by the xIdent tool to show the description of a server. The description is read-only.
